(ns diplomaform.components.reused.question)

(defn text []
  [:div {:class "form-group"}
   [:input
    {:type "text" :class "form-control" }]])

(defn radio [props]
  (for [i (:values props)]
    [:div {:class "form-check"}
     [:input
      {:id (str (:question props))
       :type "radio"
       :class "form-check-input"
       :name (str (:question props))}]
     [:label {:class "form-check-label"}
      (str i)]
     [:br]]))


(defn checkbox [props]
  (for [i (:values props)]
    [:div {:class "form-check"}
     [:input
      {:type "checkbox"
       :class "form-check-input"}]
     [:label {:class "form-check-label"} (str i)]
     [:br]]))

(defn question [props]
  [:div {:class "container"}
   [:h5 (str (:question props) (when (= (:required props) true) " *"))]
   [:form
    (when (= (:type props) (str "free-text")) (text))
    (when (= (:type props) (str "single-choice")) (radio props))
    (when (= (:type props) (str "multiple-choice")) (checkbox props))]])
